Subject: [PATCH] Add customizable date range, line chart, and period
 comparison to Dashboard

- Date-range picker on the dashboard (presets: This month / 30D / 3M / 6M /
  12M, plus custom from/to inputs) driving the /dashboard window.
- Revenue chart switched from bars to a line chart, now overlaying the
  current period against the equally-aligned previous period.
- Backend reports a comparison vs. the preceding equal-length window; Total
  Sales and Units Sold cards show an up/down % delta ("vs prev").

